description: Welcome to 206 W. 9th Street, in the heart of South Boston. This unit spans two floors of ample living space which feels much larger than the square footage depicts, and could easily be converted into a 3 bedroom if desired without losing much living space. Step inside to discover a bright and airy living space adorned with hardwood floors, wide expansive rooms, large windows, and tasteful finishes throughout. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an inviting atmosphere for both daily living and entertaining. The kitchen is large and perfect for gatherings, featuring stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, ample cabinet space, and a breakfast bar for casual dining. Enjoy outdoor living at its finest with 2 private deck's. 1 deeded driveway parking spot, Central Air Conditioning, in-unit laundry, and extra storage space complete this exceptional home.
